data.description: Excellent value on this corner lot 4BR home in Tower View Estates. The first thing you'll be impressed with is the layout. Ground floor boasts open and spacious kitchen and living space with formal dining room off the entry. Gourmet style kitchen with plenty of counter/cabinet space, stainless appliances (included), breakfast bar  and roomy eat-in nook with direct patio access. One bedroom is downstairs, along with a half bath - ideal for a guest. Remaining bedrooms and baths upstairs. Master suite bedroom is large enough for a sitting area or private desk and features a vaulted ceiling. Ensuite contemporary bath has a dual sink vanity, soaker tub and separate shower w/attractive tilework. Laundry room conveniently located upstairs. You'll also appreciate the bonus space that's just off the top floor landing - a versatile spot to arrange as office or play space, or even a secondary family room. Out back you'll enjoy a large, fenced backyard. Great location - short drive to essential shopping and major roadways (SR 27 and I4). Home shows well! Come see all that it has to offer!
